Wajen kashi 93 cikin 100 na yaran Masar masu shekaru daya zuwa 14 da haihuwa na fama da tashin hankali, in ji Khalid Darwish, mai ba da shawara ga majalisar kula da yara ta kasa da kuma Motherhood a watan Oktoba.
Karuwanci na daya daga cikin muhimman jigogin kawar da cin zarafin yara, ya kuma kara da cewa, yana mai jaddada muhimmancin hadin kai tsakanin majalisa da kuma Prosecution na Jama'a a game da haka.
