Babban jami'in Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya kai ziyara Pakistan, yana mai gabatar da batun jirgin
Islamabad (AP) - Babban magatakardan Majalisar Dinkin Duniya mai shigowa ya sanar a ranar Lahadi cewa, ya dage ziyarar da aka shirya zai kai Pakistan "saboda wasu matsalolin jirgin sama na fasaha".
An zabi shugaban jami'an diflomasiyyar Turkiyya Volkan Bozkir a zaman shugaban kasa na 75th na babban zauren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a watan da ya gabata, kuma an shirya zai isa birnin Islamabad ranar Lahadi.
Amma a wani sakon Twitter, ya ce ziyarar da babban birnin Pakistan zai kai za ta jira.
Ministan harkokin waje na kasar Pakistan Shah Mahmood Qureshi ya mayar da martani ga Bozkir yana mai cewa "Ina fatan marabtar ku zuwa kasar Pakistan nan ba da jimawa ba domin ziyarar aiki mai gina jiki da hayayyafa".
A ranar asabar da ta gabata, wani mai jubilant Qureshi, yayin da yake sanar da ziyarar, ya yi fatan zai tattauna batutuwa da dama da Bozkir, ciki har da Kashmir, wanda ya raba tsakanin Pakistan da Indiya mai makwabtaka da juna, ya kuma yi ikirarin cewa gaba ɗayansa ne.
Kasashen Pakistan da Indiya sun yi yakin basasa na biyu a yakin da suke yi da yankin da ake jayayya da shi tun bayan samun'yancin kai daga mulkin Birtaniya a shekarar 1947.
Sau da yawa bangarorin biyu na musayar wuta a Kashmir, lamarin da ya sa sojoji da fararen hula suka yi arangama a bangarorin biyu.
Pakistan na son Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta taka rawar gani wajen warware batun Kashmir a karkashin manufofinta ta hanyar barin mutanen da ke zaune a yankin Himalayan su yanke shawarar ko suna so su ci tare da Indiya, tare da Pakistan ko kuma sun fi son samun'yancin kai.
